		STOCK TICKER		








We seek believers
More than a company, we are a team that is working toward a shared mission of inspiring people to feel good, feet first. For that reason, we seek people who share our values.
People passionate about doing work that makes a difference.
People who hold themselves accountable to others and others accountable to them.
People who think a $2.6 billion company should be as creative as a start-up.
People driven by an insatiable curiosity for learning and trying new things all the time.
People who care about being the best and being among the best.
But most of all, we seek believers. People who believe remarkable things are possible and will not stop striving for them.
 
For the benefit of the people
Our people are our greatest asset. And to attract and keep the best people, we offer a package of benefits competitive with any company in the industry. These include
Choice of medical and dental and vision plans (individual, family, domestic partner)
Company-matched 401(k) savings plan
Retirement plan
Life and disability insurance
Dependent and health-care flexible spending accounts
Paid holidays and vacation
Flexible working hours
Transit and parking spending accounts
And, of course, discounts on stylish shoes!
Note: Not all associates are eligible for all benefits.
 
If you are intrigued by what you have heard and would like to learn more, please select the appropriate link and browse our open positions.


Our differences are our strengths
We’re a company that was founded on the insight that people are unique. Our founder recognized a business opportunity in diversity. And today, we see our diversity as an advantage.
We believe how we do business is every bit as important as how much business we do. And the best way to do business is for our company to be as diverse as the consumers we serve. What better way is there for us to know our customers and deliver what they truly want and need?
As a company, we are committed to employing, developing and retaining talented individuals from all backgrounds, ethnicities, genders, lifestyles and belief systems. We seek to be a company that looks and acts like the people we serve – that reflects the values and diversity of the markets in which we operate.
We believe great ideas arise from all kinds of people – in fact, the more kinds of people and the more kinds of thinking, the more we will be able to understand, anticipate and respond.
Our company is proud of its open, inclusive and collaborative environment where differences are celebrated. We invite those interested to come in and see what we have to offer.
Caleres, Inc. is an Equal Opportunity Employer and Affirmative Action Employer of minorities, women, individuals with disabilities and protected veterans. 
If you require a reasonable accommodation to access information on this website, call our Talent Team at 314.854.2495
Affirmative Action Policy Statement
Diversity, EEO and Affirmative Action Statement



