					Specialist, Social Media				
New York, NY









Specialist, Social Media
We seek a strong collaborator with exceptional communication skills and a passion for delivering engaging, on-brand assets and social content to join our Marketing team in our New York City office.
We are Caleres, a global footwear company with brands that fit people’s lives. We are ferocious about fit and living our mission of inspiring people to feel good, feet first.
We seek people who:
• Develop, curate, schedule and publish organic social content, ensuring alignment with marketing plan
• Collaborate with creative team to design social assets in line with brand style and development guidelines, incorporating best practices in social design and usability
• Track and report relevant social metrics, including reach, clicks, engagement, revenue and content performance
• Audit competitive and industry data, and monitor trends in social media tools, applications, channels, design and strategy
• Lead social innovation by developing progressive social media programs and expanding our brand portfolio social footprint into new and relevant social platforms
We seek people with these qualifications:
• Bachelor’s degree in Marketing, Communications or Digital Media
• 3+ years experience in social media planning and execution preferred
• 3+ years design and social back-end development experience preferred
• Experience ideating compelling blog content, reaching out to and evaluating influencers
• Passionate about growing followership in core social media channels – Instagram, Facebook, Pinterest & Twitter
• Excellent verbal and written communication skills with ability to pitch concepts to internal brand teams
• Proficient in Adobe Illustrator, Photoshop, InDesign & Acrobat
But most of all, we seek believers. People who share our values and our ferocity for fit.
People passionate about their work. People who hold themselves and others accountable. People who think a $2.6 billion company should be as creative as a start-up. People driven by an insatiable curiosity. People who care about being the best, among the best. 
People who believe remarkable things are possible and will not stop striving for them.
Become a believer.
EOE/M/F/Vet/Disabled

