•	Assist cross-functional teams in the implementation of projects and initiatives affecting store programs and systems, ensuring our store teams are able to connect with our customers
•	Act as subject matter expert for operational standards, policies, procedures and compliance requirements for our Famous Footwear & Naturalizer stores
•	Partner with IT and other internal teams to support the development, testing and rollout of field system enhancements
•	Analyze data to evaluate the success of store initiatives, identifying opportunities for process improvements to enhance efficiency and execution
