•	3-5 years retail experience preferred
•	Exceptional communication and collaboration skills
•	Self-motivated, innovative problem-solver
•	Excellent project management and prioritization skills with ability to meet multiple competing deadlines
•	Advanced proficiency in Microsoft Excel
•	Working knowledge of SAP and IBM iSeries systems a plus
