Diversity, EEO and Affirmative Action Statement






New York: City of the World
A city of the world pulsing with the passion of eight million creative human beings.
As a global leader in footwear and lifestyle brands in key market segments, Caleres thrives on the vibrancy, hustle, bustle and diversity of New York. And that energy infuses what we do — bringing a cosmopolitan caché to our designs, challenging us to broaden our horizons, up our game and take it out on the world stage.
They say if you can make it here you can make it anywhere. With the spirit of New York to inspire us, we’re confident we can make it everywhere.
 


St. Louis: City of Pioneers
St. Louis – the original home of our company – is the global headquarters of Caleres.
St. Louis was founded by pioneers – can-do people, men and women of determined spirit pursuing the American dream. That same spirit was imbued in our founder and still permeates our company today. Even as we grow every year, offering more brands in more countries and serving more consumers than ever before, we’ll always have one foot firmly planted in St. Louis.
 


Dongguan, China: Manufacturing Expertise and Global Supply Chain
China is the world leader in manufacturing. And Dongguan is the manufacturing leader in China. Established in south Guangdong province more than 5,000 years ago, in modern times Dongguan has become responsible for more than $65 billion in annual exports.
Within our company, the Dongguan office provides industry-leading knowledge and expertise in manufacturing, production, global supply chain management and much more. We draw on the energy and expertise of Dongguan to bring the vision of Caleres to life.
 








