Caleres, Inc. Key Developments

Caleres Appoints Malcolm Robinson as President to New Men’s and International Division
Jul 13 17
Caleres announced the appointment of Malcolm Robinson as president of the company’s new Men’s and International division. He will oversee the strategic growth initiatives for the Caleres men’s brands, as well as expand an international footprint across the company’s portfolio. Robinson most recently served as EVP at One Jeanswear Group - William Rast Division. There he was responsible for the overall in-store marketing and sales strategy of the licensed William Rast denim lifestyle brand. A significant portion of his career was spent as group president of wholesale sportswear at Phillips Van Heusen. He was also an executive vice president at Gant Corporation.


Caleres, Inc. Presents at NRF Protect 2017 Loss Prevention Conference & EXPO, Jun-26-2017
Jun 26 17
Caleres, Inc. Presents at NRF Protect 2017 Loss Prevention Conference & EXPO, Jun-26-2017 . Venue: Gaylord National Harbor Hotel, Washington, United States.


Caleres, Inc. Announces Regular Quarterly Dividend , Payable on July 3, 2017
Jun 7 17
Caleres, Inc. announced a quarterly dividend of $0.07 per share. The dividend will be payable on July 3, 2017, to shareholders of record as of June 19, 2017.


